{"tid":843124,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"［新手上路］想問究竟無反黎講APC-S好啲定M4/3好啲","createTime":"2018-10-01T02:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T11:09:26.000Z","uid":33391,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"9ef552e3617edaf5aef14fa512cfc02797406ffd","tid":843124,"uid":33391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T02:08:23.000Z","msg":"上網睇好多人都捧M4/3又輕又平 畫質又靚<br />\n但係唔係幾明點解M4/3細啲但係會高畫質過APC-S<br />\n同埋M4/3嘅高ISO同對對焦方面係咪會差啲？<br />\n<br />\n有講錯嘅請指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2533bc7999e4c56dd83eab0f9b08e9edcf1411a","tid":843124,"uid":208689,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T02:11:58.000Z","msg":"連Panasonic都開始出ff機<br />\n咁你估下m43未來會有咩前景"},{"pid":"feb76796b9d0ee6935f55656a998d230077bf86f","tid":843124,"uid":50502,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T02:17:41.000Z","msg":"理論上sensor 愈大愈好 m43 唔會好過apsc<br />\n咪聽班m43 撚屌鳩up iphone 夠有人話影到靚相啦 仲買乜撚相機"},{"pid":"cbad5121886bef18eb6482cd32bd4460c9188451","tid":843124,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T02:22:09.000Z","msg":"200d啦屌"},{"pid":"6aec6af6757a5456a087be5752c20cc4a7224e45","tid":843124,"uid":22046,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T02:25:23.000Z","msg":"畫質高唔高多數睇鏡頭<br />\n但apsc 先天條件比m43好一級"},{"pid":"7aad348d12956f66ac0f2f31af7ab72ddd799967","tid":843124,"uid":33391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T02:37:24.000Z","msg":"係咪太多m43打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到有人話m43個cmos密度大啲所以畫質好靚"},{"pid":"3492065ab1236d2701eedf31200793bd163cc4ff","tid":843124,"uid":7057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T02:41:00.000Z","msg":"m43 廢左嫁啦。根本唔上唔落冇人用"},{"pid":"5ada1c900bb96b63cfcebd0275f9b2180137fd0e","tid":843124,"uid":50502,"like":3,"dislike